videos.description: Amber Smith gets the inbound pass and takes it to the rack, finishing through contact for the Tigers.
videos.headline: Mizzou's Smith attacks the rim

videos.description: Cierra Porter displays beautiful post moves getting the and-1 layup to fall in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Missouri's Porter does work in the paint

videos.description: Sophie Cunningham gets creative, knocking down the underhanded layup high off the glass.
videos.headline: Mizzou's Cunningham hits acrobatic layup

videos.description: Gamecocks' head coach Dawn Staley is ejected in the fourth quarter after receiving her second technical foul.
videos.headline: South Carolina head coach ejected from game
